6327:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC oversampling discontinuous mode (triggered mode)
6328:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         on the selected ADC group.
