7052:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         without ADC disable command on going.
7053:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @rmtoll CR       ADSTP          LL_ADC_REG_StopConversion
